snippet.title: Sonic Blast Man 2 Game Sample - SNES/SFC
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: December 22nd, 2008

What can be largely considered an improvement over the first game, this game threw in the only thing I really cared about that the original lacked; A co-op mode. The two new characters and enhanced fighting engine make this game a fun beat-em-up. It's significantly harder to find than the first game.
